public static class BossImageSearchServiceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder

Attribute map builder for the BossImageSearchService component. You can use this builder as a type-safe alternative to populating the attribute map using attribute keys.

serviceURI

public BossImageSearchServiceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder serviceURI(String value)
Boss Image search service URI. Specifies the URI at which Yahoo Boss Image Search API is available. The ${query} place holder will be replaced with the URL-encoded text of the processed query.

dimensions

public BossImageSearchServiceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder dimensions(Dimensions value)
The size of images to fetch. Small images are generally thumbnail or icon sized. Medium sized images are average sized; usually not exceeding an average screen size. Large images are screen size or larger.
